{"id": "1370275520620662814", "channel_id": "1370075486235000932", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "1.5-Year Anniversary Preview: System Optimizations\nDear Keepers,\nWelcome to our second preview of the 1.5 Anniversary Update!\nThis time, we're focusing on system optimizations, including the long-awaited Phonograph feature and enhanced rewards, all designed to elevate your gameplay experience.\nNew additions include: Commemorative Wheel of Destiny exchange, streamlined new player guidance, and improved English gameplay text translations (to help players worldwide better navigate Morimens!)\n\nNote: Final features are subject to in-game release.\n\n[Phonograph Unlocked]\nRelive Mythag's original soundtracks through the new Phonograph!\nUnlock 1/3 of a chapter's OST by clearing its Normal Mode stages.\nUnlock another 1/3 by completing Hard Mode.\nUse Reality Verge to unlock the remaining tracks.\n※More OST collections will be continuously updated. Stay tuned!\n\n[New Free Rewards]\nExtra SSR Wheels of Destiny/Awakener Shards now convert into Gnosis Fragment ×3 + Refined Gnosis Fragment ×1.\nIn-Sheath Supply now provides Remembrance Quill ×30 daily in addition to Menophin.\nCurriculum: Doubled Remembrance Quill rewards for both Basic & Advanced Topics at Level 50.\nAlumni Donations Rewards: Now includes Refined Gnosis Primers, Aetheric Stones, Formless One's Vouchers, plus double the amount of Remembrance Quills.\n※All new rewards will be retroactively distributed via mail post-update!\n\n[Commemorative Wheel of Destiny Returns]\nThe 1st Anniversary Limited SSR Wheel \"Heart of Silver\" is now available in the Radix Sediment Exchange!\nMissed it last time? Here's your chance to claim it.\n\n[New Player Tutorial Improvements]\nPrologue to Chapter 2 now feature more detailed guides, helping new Keepers start their journey smoothly.", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T05:45:42.604000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": true, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370075486235000932", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～系统优化篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1370275529961508874", "channel_id": "1370075486235000932", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "[English Language Support]\nCombat-related terms will be unified for clarity.\nDetailed pre- and post-localization glossaries will be released for Attributes, Skills, Effects, Orisons, and Relics.\nWe're committed to keep refining text flow, phrasing, and UI readability—this is just the beginning!\n※Full translation of upcoming story/UI content is still in progress.", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T05:45:44.831000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": true, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370075486235000932", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：1.5周年～系统优化篇", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
